<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 02:22:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将在美国国会联席会议上发表讲话；特朗普告诉支持者：许多以色列人质已经死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article-live/netanyahu-to-address-joint-session-of-u-s-congress-trump-many-israeli-hostages-are-dead/0000018f-a83e-d8a2-a3cf-acbfde440000</link><description>以色列在一天的火箭弹和无人机袭击北部边境社区后袭击了黎巴嫩南部的真主党目标 ■ 内塔尼亚胡：安全机构没有就来自加沙的哈马斯袭击发出警告，事实恰恰相反 ■ 以色列谴责爱尔兰、挪威、西班牙特使就巴勒斯坦举动 ■ 欧盟外交政策负责人：所有欧盟捐助者恢复对近东救济工程处的资助</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 01:47:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article-live/netanyahu-to-address-joint-session-of-u-s-congress-trump-many-israeli-hostages-are-dead/0000018f-a83e-d8a2-a3cf-acbfde440000</guid></item><item><title>“让你的学校难堪”：大学领导因屈服于“亲哈马斯”团体而受到共和党议员的欺凌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/university-leaders-get-bullied-by-republican-lawmakers-for-caving-in-to-pro-hamas-groups/0000018f-a735-dfc6-a3ef-b77d24480000</link><description>在三个多小时的艰苦审讯中，西北大学、罗格斯大学和加州大学洛杉矶分校的校长因没有更强有力地镇压在校园内未经授权设立营地的反以色列抗议者而受到严厉批评。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 21:03:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/university-leaders-get-bullied-by-republican-lawmakers-for-caving-in-to-pro-hamas-groups/0000018f-a735-dfc6-a3ef-b77d24480000</guid></item><item><title>国会接待内塔尼亚胡并不是“亲以色列”，内塔尼亚胡被半数以上的国家鄙视</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-23/ty-article/.highlight/its-not-pro-israel-for-congress-to-host-netanyahu-despised-more-than-half-his-country/0000018f-a665-d476-a7df-e76d6bb70000</link><description>在国会面前发表讲话只是内塔尼亚胡宁愿做的另一件事，而不是面对 10 月 7 日之前遭受毁灭性打击的以色列人</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 19:47:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-23/ty-article/.highlight/its-not-pro-israel-for-congress-to-host-netanyahu-despised-more-than-half-his-country/0000018f-a665-d476-a7df-e76d6bb70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战时内阁同意继续与哈马斯进行人质谈判，但消息人士对谈判是否成功表示怀疑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-war-cabinet-okays-continuation-of-talks-with-hamas-as-sources-doubtful-of-success/0000018f-a651-d8a2-a3cf-a6d394090000</link><description>熟悉战时内阁部长讨论情况的消息人士称，谈判小组有一定的回旋余地，但很快达成协议释放人质的可能性很低</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 17:59:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-war-cabinet-okays-continuation-of-talks-with-hamas-as-sources-doubtful-of-success/0000018f-a651-d8a2-a3cf-a6d394090000</guid></item><item><title>参议员乔什·霍利：关于共和党、以色列和反犹太主义的案例研究</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/sen-josh-hawley-a-case-study-on-the-republicans-israel-and-antisemitism/0000018f-a591-d1e2-a1ff-afbf050f0000</link><description>自2018年当选以来，这位密苏里州参议员已经从持有传统的鹰派观点，转变为唐纳德·特朗普和塔克·卡尔森倡导的孤立主义“美国优先”方针。不过，他对反犹太主义比喻的使用更加一致</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 17:26:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/sen-josh-hawley-a-case-study-on-the-republicans-israel-and-antisemitism/0000018f-a591-d1e2-a1ff-afbf050f0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人对西班牙、爱尔兰和挪威的国家承认感到高兴，但也有些愤世嫉俗。</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-react-with-joy-and-some-cynicism-to-state-recognition-by-european-countries/0000018f-a5ac-d0b4-a3cf-b7ace61a0000</link><description>尽管巴勒斯坦官方渠道感谢挪威、爱尔兰和西班牙承认巴勒斯坦国的决定，但网上的一些人提出了更多质疑</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 17:08:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-react-with-joy-and-some-cynicism-to-state-recognition-by-european-countries/0000018f-a5ac-d0b4-a3cf-b7ace61a0000</guid></item><item><title>英国提前大选意味着英国犹太人和穆斯林将度过丑陋的六周</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/u-k-snap-election-means-six-ugly-weeks-for-british-jews-and-muslims/0000018f-a60f-d9c2-af8f-b7df4e7e0000</link><description>下届英国大选结果对加沙战争的影响力为零。但保守党和极左翼都希望通过将其注入竞选活动中，向工党领袖凯尔·斯塔默施加压力，并使穆斯林选民反对他</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 17:01:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/u-k-snap-election-means-six-ugly-weeks-for-british-jews-and-muslims/0000018f-a60f-d9c2-af8f-b7df4e7e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 230 天：埃及消息人士称，以色列仍未准备好进行人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-230-israel-still-not-ready-for-hostage-deal-egyptian-source-says/0000018f-a655-d476-a7df-e77d73380001</link><description>战时内阁指示以色列谈判团队与哈马斯进行进一步谈判 ■ 以色列国防军调查发现，以色列军队上周在加沙无意中杀害了联合国援助人员 ■ 以色列国防军表示，2023 年 3 月至 7 月期间，内塔尼亚胡总理收到了来自军事情报部门的四份单独的书面警告，称以色列的内部危机鼓励伊朗、真主党和哈马斯采取行动反对它 ■ 这是战争 230 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 16:51:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-230-israel-still-not-ready-for-hostage-deal-egyptian-source-says/0000018f-a655-d476-a7df-e77d73380001</guid></item><item><title>十月后，与犹太以色列人相比，阿拉伯以色列人患创伤后应激障碍、焦虑和抑郁的风险更大。 7、研究发现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/arabs-at-greater-risk-of-ptsd-compared-to-jews-in-israel-post-oct-7-study-finds/0000018f-a605-d1e2-a1ff-ae2f49440000</link><description>鲁宾学术中心的研究人员发现，与犹太人相比，阿拉伯人患 PTSD 的可能性高出约 2.5 倍，患抑郁症的可能性高出约 1.7 倍，患焦虑症的可能性高出 6.4 倍</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 16:21:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/arabs-at-greater-risk-of-ptsd-compared-to-jews-in-israel-post-oct-7-study-finds/0000018f-a605-d1e2-a1ff-ae2f49440000</guid></item><item><title>当这些以色列士兵在加沙死亡时，他们的同性恋身份也随之消失</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-these-israeli-soldiers-died-in-gaza-their-gay-identity-died-with-them/0000018f-9fc1-da35-a3af-dfeb78f20000</link><description>“诺姆的家人只是想埋葬一切，隐藏他的身份和身份”：他们的同性恋伴侣在加沙的死亡意味着这些失去亲人的伴侣必须独自应对这一损失，没有周围人或国家的支持</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 15:15:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-these-israeli-soldiers-died-in-gaza-their-gay-identity-died-with-them/0000018f-9fc1-da35-a3af-dfeb78f20000</guid></item><item><title>我父亲是加沙的人质。巴勒斯坦人不是我的敌人——盲目的仇恨才是</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-father-is-a-hostage-in-gaza-palestinians-are-not-my-enemy/0000018f-a4a7-dca3-a7cf-a5b721d30000</link><description>当我们流血和悲伤时，对于像我自己这样的家庭来说，我们对亲人的命运悬在希望和绝望之间，有时我想大喊，极左派对以色列的沾沾自喜的仇恨是徒劳的。我们迫切需要的是他们对为正义与和平而努力的以色列人和巴勒斯坦人的支持</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 14:44:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-father-is-a-hostage-in-gaza-palestinians-are-not-my-enemy/0000018f-a4a7-dca3-a7cf-a5b721d30000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡否认以色列军队在10月7日之前警告他哈马斯打算袭击以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-denies-the-idf-warned-him-before-oct-7-of-hamas-intention-to-attack-israel/0000018f-a5b0-d0b4-a3cf-b7bc32b10000</link><description>以色列国防军周四证实，在加沙战争爆发之前，它曾警告总理内塔尼亚胡，司法改革引发的危机正在鼓励伊朗、真主党和哈马斯冒对以色列采取潜在行动的风险</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 14:30:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-denies-the-idf-warned-him-before-oct-7-of-hamas-intention-to-attack-israel/0000018f-a5b0-d0b4-a3cf-b7bc32b10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列妇女试图将山羊偷偷带进圣殿山献祭，导致山羊死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/goat-dies-as-israeli-woman-attempts-to-sneak-it-into-temple-mount-for-sacrifice/0000018f-a54f-d8a2-a3cf-a5cfbedf0000</link><description>当这只山羊开始在耶路撒冷老城入口处的女子衣服下走动并发出噪音时，警方接到了警报。在极右翼部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔的支持下，走私动物献祭的企图有所增加</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 14:20:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/goat-dies-as-israeli-woman-attempts-to-sneak-it-into-temple-mount-for-sacrifice/0000018f-a54f-d8a2-a3cf-a5cfbedf0000</guid></item><item><title>黄金耶路撒冷：这是以色列首都出售的最昂贵的公寓</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-of-gold-luxury-penthouse-sets-new-price-record-in-israels-capital/0000018f-a4f1-d8a2-a3cf-a4f3bd850000</link><description>该住宅以 1700 万美元的价格出售给计划移民的非以色列人，每平方米的价格为 30,750 美元。它毗邻一座建于 20 世纪 50 年代的历史豪宅</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 13:18:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-of-gold-luxury-penthouse-sets-new-price-record-in-israels-capital/0000018f-a4f1-d8a2-a3cf-a4f3bd850000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方起诉两名极右翼抗议者袭击失去亲人的父亲</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-indict-two-far-right-protesters-for-assault-of-bereaved-israeli-father/0000018f-a4d5-dca3-a7cf-a5f5160c0000</link><description>加迪·凯德姆 (Gadi Kedem) 在哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击中失去了六名家人，他在特拉维夫的一次集会上抗议释放加沙的人质时遭到袭击。据称，一名袭击者大喊“你的孩子被杀了，真好，左派！”凯德姆的妻子</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 12:45:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-indict-two-far-right-protesters-for-assault-of-bereaved-israeli-father/0000018f-a4d5-dca3-a7cf-a5f5160c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军调查发现以色列军队违反规定，误杀拉法的联合国援助人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/idf-probe-israeli-forces-breached-regulations-mistakenly-killed-un-aid-worker-in-gaza/0000018f-a50e-db21-a9ff-b53eaf700000</link><description>以色列国防军上周对一名联合国工作人员死亡事件进行的调查发现，他的车辆在没有以色列国防军协调的情况下行驶在禁行道路上。尽管标有联合国字母 - 并且违反了有关人道主义工作者的规定 - 该车辆首先遭到炮弹袭击，然后在附近遭到手榴弹袭击</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/idf-probe-israeli-forces-breached-regulations-mistakenly-killed-un-aid-worker-in-gaza/0000018f-a50e-db21-a9ff-b53eaf700000</guid></item><item><title>以色列为期两天的约旦河西岸行动造成12名巴勒斯坦人死亡、25人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/12-palestinians-killed-25-wounded-in-israels-two-day-jenin-operation/0000018f-a536-df13-a3af-b536d3a80000</link><description>军方周二在杰宁市和邻近的城市难民营发起了这次行动，作为镇压该地区武装分子的一部分。巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战武装组织表示，其战士与以色列军队作战</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 11:48:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/12-palestinians-killed-25-wounded-in-israels-two-day-jenin-operation/0000018f-a536-df13-a3af-b536d3a80000</guid></item><item><title>谁害怕承认巴勒斯坦国？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/whos-afraid-of-recognizing-a-palestinian-state/0000018f-a496-d8a2-a3cf-a49735d50000</link><description>即使巴勒斯坦国是一个正在形成的“失败国家”，它仍然是以色列必须考虑的问题。你不能像本杰明·内塔尼亚胡试图做的那样，通过完全否定辩论和进程来塑造和影响辩论和进程</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 11:09:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/whos-afraid-of-recognizing-a-palestinian-state/0000018f-a496-d8a2-a3cf-a49735d50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内盖夫沙漠教堂发现早期基督教船只涂鸦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-05-23/ty-article/early-christian-ship-graffiti-found-at-church-in-israels-negev-desert/0000018f-a4ce-d639-a5bf-f7fe1d940000</link><description>在南部城市拉哈特的一个新社区的建设过程中，考古学家发现了六世纪的教堂，上面有可能将朝圣者带到圣地的船只的照片</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 10:34:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-05-23/ty-article/early-christian-ship-graffiti-found-at-church-in-israels-negev-desert/0000018f-a4ce-d639-a5bf-f7fe1d940000</guid></item><item><title>崩溃还是认可？巴勒斯坦领导人面临关键时刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/on-verge-of-collapse-and-recognition-the-palestinian-leadership-faces-a-moment-of-truth/0000018f-a482-db21-a9ff-b4bec6b90000</link><description>欧洲国家承认巴勒斯坦国主要是对加沙局势的回应。但如果西岸的巴勒斯坦领导层不寻求变革，即使获得更多国家的承认也不会改变当地的局势</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 10:27:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/on-verge-of-collapse-and-recognition-the-palestinian-leadership-faces-a-moment-of-truth/0000018f-a482-db21-a9ff-b4bec6b90000</guid></item></channel></rss>